'''Chicago Jewish News''' is a newspaper mainly serving the [[Jews in Chicago|Jewish population in Chicago]]. The newspaper won two [[Simon Rockower Award]]s in 2015, where it is categorized as a newspaper with a [[Newspaper circulation|circulation]] of less than 15.000 copies.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ajpa.org/?page=2015Rockower|title=The 34th Annual Simon Rockower Award Winners|accessdate=2016-12-04}}</ref> The newspaper states a readership of over 40,000.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chicagojewishnews.com/advertise/|title=The Chicago Jewish News - To Advertise|accessdate=2016-12-04}}</ref>
