ael Wright]]: portrait painter in the Baroque style<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.npg.org.uk/collections/search/person/mp07767/john-michael-wright |title=Person - National Portrait Gallery |publisher= |accessdate=24 March 2017}}</ref>
